e":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":180,"height":180,"src":"/static/1349b0961c84fc03397d8b4f910c987b/12688/kartik.jpg","srcSet":"/static/1349b0961c84fc03397d8b4f910c987b/12688/kartik.jpg 1x,\n/static/1349b0961c84fc03397d8b4f910c987b/33613/kartik.jpg 1.5x","srcWebp":"/static/1349b0961c84fc03397d8b4f910c987b/79a97/kartik.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/1349b0961c84fc03397d8b4f910c987b/79a97/kartik.webp 1x,\n/static/1349b0961c84fc03397d8b4f910c987b/a2081/kartik.webp 1.5x"}}},"social":{"facebook":"","instagram":"","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kartik-jhakal/","twitter":"","youtube":""}}},"html":"<p>Blogging has come a long way and nowadays many people are living a life by choosing to blog as a full-time career option. But is it so easy?</p>\n<p>Yes, setting up a blog and start blogging is actually very simple.</p>\n<p>But to make money from blogging is not at all an easy task at all. One will need huge knowledge, time to experiment, and skills to write &#x26; convince the audience.</p>\n<p>Due to the technology evolution, you now have seamless options to create a blog. You can check our series of 'Create Superfast blogs' using Gatsby, Jekyll, Hugo, Hexo, Next JS, WordPress, and using blogger.</p>\n<p><strong>Before you get to any of those, you must first identify the most profitable blog niches for you.</strong></p>\n<p>Find your knowledge area and write about what you are passionate about. You will defiantly get this great advice from experts when you’re searching for a niche to start your <a href=\"https://www.entrepreneur.com/topic/blog\">blog</a>. But, this is not enough. The key to <a href=\"https://www.entrepreneur.com/video/307493\">building a successful blog</a> is finding a “profitable” niche.</p>\n<p>Finding the perfect niche is the most crucial and first step of building a blog that often gets overlooked. If you pick a niche with too much competition, your blog will get beaten down by high authority blogs and if you pick a niche with no demand, your blog will barely make an impact and earn anything for you. You should find a niche that’s in the middle and a niche that can also be monetized easily.</p>\n<p>Remember the best formula for a profitable Niche -</p>\n<p><strong>Profitable Niche = No too much competition + Niche in Demand + High-income Potential</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4821210a7837ad6b4cd97dac95c7549/2bef9/niche-2-circle-venn-diagram-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"best formula to find a profitable Niche\"\n        title=\"best formula to find a profitable Niche\"\n        src=\"/static/f4821210a7837ad6b4cd97dac95c7549/2bef9/niche-2-circle-venn-diagram-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f4821210a7837ad6b4cd97dac95c7549/e85cb/niche-2-circle-venn-diagram-1.png 480w,\n/static/f4821210a7837ad6b4cd97dac95c7549/d9199/niche-2-circle-venn-diagram-1.png 960w,\n/static/f4821210a7837ad6b4cd97dac95c7549/2bef9/niche-2-circle-venn-diagram-1.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>In this blog post, we’ll give you practical tips on how to find a profitable niche that can generate traffic and eventually turn into a successful income stream.</p>\n<p>Create an <a href=\"\">excel sheet</a> with the following questions. I will explain this template at the last of the article.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: What Makes any Niche a Good Niche?</h3>\n<p>When you are searching for ideas for your niches, there are several things to look for. A good niche should be one where:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Consumers are facing problems in</li>\n<li>Consumers are willing to spend money online</li>\n<li>There are products that you can promote or sell</li>\n<li>You have a decent understanding of</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Alright, let’s break it down, starting with the first criteria… consumers in your niche should be willing to spend money online.</p>\n<p>To earn money in any business have a very simple formula that also applied here.</p>\n<p><strong>Value Delivered to your Audience/Customer = Success</strong></p>\n<p>Step 1 Research</p>\n<p>Step 2 Research</p>\n<p>Step 3 and more research </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1_1p_aWVQyJde0TvQyc_7y2aPoUfUt0ThMJ1QkhzzsWg/edit?usp=sharing\" title=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1_1p_aWVQyJde0TvQyc_7y2aPoUfUt0ThMJ1QkhzzsWg/edit?usp=sharing\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1<em>1p</em>aWVQyJde0TvQyc_7y2aPoUfUt0ThMJ1QkhzzsWg/edit?usp=sharing</a></p>\n<p>1- Do a Research</p>\n<p>Make a large list</p>\n<p>Filter the list</p>\n<p>Select the niche</p>\n<p>2-</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"steps-to-find-perfect-and-profitable-blog-topicniche-with-example-and-niche-finding-tool"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1408454471","2402320237","2404490943","2661970575","3704789613","3904292974","399170485","4034318880","493794765","63159454","717698143","850277546"]}